description: The man was seen leaving a property in the Isle of Man after police responded to reports of a party.
title: Coronavirus Isle of Man: Douglas partygoer jailed for lockdown breach
title_page: Coronavirus Isle of Man: Douglas partygoer jailed for lockdown breach - BBC News
maintext: He told police he had been locked out of his own flat the night before and had decided to stay with a "friend of a friend" at the address.
